reviewText:
I love 50's 60's and 70's sci fi, its what I grew up on.  This however... wow what a dog!  Never did finish watching the whole
thing. it was that bad.  DO NOT WASTE YOUR MONEY...  go flush your toilet and watch that, it will be more entertaining.

Please, do not waste your money on this awful film! The package is "nice", almost no information on the back though. The film itself is trash. Very, very old, poor condition, horrible acting, no plot, color fades in and out, lots of scratches and dust spots. Worst purchase I've made on Amazon.
A cult classic b-movie science fiction that deserves watching!
It says the is a 2016 film.  Maybe a 1956 film.  What the hell?
